Prerequisite: Have JRE 1.8 installed, git to clone repository and Putty as simple client.

Step 1: Clone repository from github in a directory i.e. C:\Dev\simple-chat
Step 2: Compile the code with command "javac *.java"
Step 3: Start chat server with command "java net.amoriconi.Main"
Step 4: Open an instance of putty then make a raw connection to localhost at port 10000, in the console output a message confirm that a new
        client is connected.
Step 5: Open a second instance of putty and make a connection like previous step.
Step 6: Now from the first instance of putty write the message "This is a test message" then press Enter, the message will be broadcasted to
        the second instance of Putty.
